data.description: LOCATION!! Home is one of the most private lots in the community. Home like new and well maintained. 3 CAR GARAGE! Home is a 4 bedroom with a HUGE BONUS ROOM or make it a 5 bedroom if you prefer. Beautiful backyard with farm views. Lot next to the home cannot be built on, giving you extra privacy! This home features TWO master bedrooms, one downstairs and one upstairs. TWO dining areas - formal dining can be used as a home office. Master closet downstairs is everyone's DREAM! All bedrooms have large walk in closets. The walk in laundry room features a drop zone and a tile accent wall. No shortage of storage in this home!! Natural light flows throughout! Kitchen features granite countertops , shaker style white cabinets and a custom tile backsplash with a huge walk in pantry! Convenient to I-40 and 210 HWY. This home is a must see!
